Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.resource

Class ResourceDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.resource.ResourceDto
public class ResourceDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for resource information. This class encapsulates all relevant details about a resource, including its identifier, type, name, description, observations, brand, serial number, supplier name, supplier contact, and old supplier name.
